Package net.ssehub.comani.core

Class Setup

java.lang.Object
net.ssehub.comani.core.Setup
public class Setup
extends java.lang.Object
This class reads the configuration file and provides the user-defined properties for other components of the tool.
Author:
Christian Kroeher
